Decision-maserver creation -nodejs + Express

Basic commands
--------------

1)Creating package.json -npm init
2)Creating node modules -npm i express (insatall express)
3)install nodemon -npm install -g nodemon
4)run - nodemon index.js


Basic steps
------------

1)Creating a folder (Bankserver)
2)Creatin package.json file
3)install express
4)import express inside the index.js file
5)Create an app using express
6)Setip the port number
7)resolving htp request king skills

8)HTTP Response code 
   1xx-information
   2xx-successful
   3xx-redirection
   4xx-client error
   5xx-server error

9)JWT Token
install jwt token - npm i jsonwebtoken
to generate token - sign()


10) middleware
it comes in the middle of the request and response cyle 0of thr nodejs execution
    req,res,next

    1)Application specific middleware- for entire application
    2)Router specific middleware- for token verification -verify()
    







12)Database integration
      1)install mongoose - npm i mongoose

13)Asynchronous function resolving - promise
   
   1)Resolve state - .then()
   2)Reject state - catch()

14)CORS - Cross origin resource sharing
  
   install cors- npm i cors

   port 4200(Angular) ----request----> 3000(node)(recieve)

15) Asynchronous call - RxJs - (Reactive Extension for JavaScript)

JS - promise

TS - RxJs(library)

 1)Observable 
   a)resolved - subscribe()
   b)reject - catch()




